name: Ether Haikus #6
description: This series of works contemplate the universe through the substance of ether. A pleasant smelling colorless liquid. Often used as an anesthesia. It has also come to embody the idea of paradise and the cosmos. The celestial composition of the animations allude to a deciphering of the sublime. A message received and pinged onto earth by the agents of Copy Planet. Cooked by collaborating with artist Salafurka.
